Class FAQ

java.lang.Object
model.FAQ
public class FAQ extends Object
Model class representing a Frequently Asked Question (FAQ) entry. Each FAQ links to a question and contains display metadata such as category, title, staff notes, and the staff member who marked it.

      public FAQ(int questionId, String category, String displayTitle, String staffNotes, int markedByStaffId)
      Constructor used when creating a new FAQ (ID auto-generated).
      Parameters:
      questionId - ID of the related question
      category - FAQ category (e.g. "General", "Technical")
      displayTitle - Display title shown in the FAQ list
      staffNotes - Optional notes left by the staff
      markedByStaffId - ID of the staff/admin who created the FAQ
